@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mcoayy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.21 + wp.exp((tmp + 0.89 * v2 + 0.41)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (v2 * v2)
    tmp = wp.exp((v2 - (tmp + 0.13 * v0 + 0.28)))
    v2 = 0.97
    data[tid] = v0
